text: Michaela Moťovská is a Slovak football defender, currently playing for Sparta Praha in the Czech First Division.Profile in Sparta's website She is a member of the Slovakia national team.Statistics at UEFA website She made her debut for the national team on 7 August 2015 in a match against United Arab Emirates. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Michaela Motovska - Slovak Defender 2015 on YouTube Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak women's footballers Category:Expatriate women's footballers in the Czech Republic Category:Slovak expatriate footballers Category:Slovak footballers Category:People from Šaľa Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Slovak expatriate sportspeople in the Czech Republic Category:AC Sparta Praha (women) players Category:Slovakia women's international footballers Category:Czech First Division (women) players
